title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 7/7 - Grimm/Krawczynski
description: Voice of Gophers football Mike Grimm joins Nordo to break down USC & UCLA joining the Big 10 & the Gophers upcoming season.  Plus, Jon Krawczynski calls in to discuss Rudy Gobert's introductory press conference, the Wolves going big, & more!
